'''2020－2021年亞美尼亞示威'''始於[[亞美尼亞|亞美尼亞]]和[[阿塞拜疆|亞塞拜然]]於2020年11月10日簽署[[2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫停火協議|2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫停火協議]]後<ref>{{cite web|url=https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1037906.html|title=Anti-Pashinyan demonstrators rally in “March of Dignity”|work=[[Armenpress|Armenpress]]|date=15 December 2020|accessdate=16 December 2020|archive-date=2020-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201216173332/https://armenpress.am/eng/news/1037906.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，亞美尼亞總理[[尼科尔·帕希尼扬|尼科爾·帕希尼揚]]在[[Facebook|Facebook]]上宣布他簽署了停火協議，協議內容中[[亚美尼亚武装力量|亞美尼亞軍隊]]將會撤出並放棄亞美尼亞在[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|納卡戰爭]]後佔領的亞塞拜然領土，這當中包括了[[亞美尼亞控制的納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫周邊地區|納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫周邊地區]]。成千上萬的[[亚美尼亚人|亞美尼亞人]]上街抗議，數百人衝進首都[[葉里溫|葉里溫]]的[[亞美尼亞國會大樓|國會大廈]]並要求簽署協議的總理帕希尼揚下台。<ref name=":0">{{cite news|last1=Kramer|first1=Andrew E.|title=Facing Military Debacle, Armenia Accepts a Deal in Nagorno-Karabakh War|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/09/world/middleeast/armenia-settlement-nagorno-karabakh-azerbaijan.html|accessdate=2020-11-10|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2020-11-10|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110011006/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/09/world/middleeast/armenia-settlement-nagorno-karabakh-azerbaijan.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>亚美尼亚国会议长{{tsl|en|Ararat Mirzoyan|阿拉拉特·米尔佐扬}}被闯入议会的示威者殴打。事後米尔佐扬接受手术治療<ref>{{cite news |title=Armenian parliament speaker injured by protesters, prime minister says |url=https://tass.com/world/1221775 |accessdate=2020-11-12 |work=TASS |date=2020-11-09 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170918/https://tass.com/world/1221775 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Armenian parliament speaker assaulted by angry protesters after peace deal, undergoes surgery |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/world/story/armenian-parliament-speaker-assaulted-by-angry-protesters-over-peace-deal-undergoes-surgery-1739576-2020-11-10 |accessdate=2020-11-12 |work=India Today |date=2020-11-10 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115170918/https://www.indiatoday.in/world/story/armenian-parliament-speaker-assaulted-by-angry-protesters-over-peace-deal-undergoes-surgery-1739576-2020-11-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2021年2月25日，[[亚美尼亚武装力量总参谋长|亞美尼亞武裝部隊總參]]發佈備忘錄要求總理[[尼科尔·帕希尼扬|尼科尔·帕希尼扬]]辭職下台，但帕辛揚譴責這是一次[[2021年亞美尼亞未遂政變|未遂的軍事政變]]。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-02-25|title=Armenia’s PM says call for his resignation are attempted coup|url=https://english.alarabiya.net/News/world/2021/02/25/Armenian-PM-says-attempted-coup-happening-in-the-country-Report|access-date=2021-02-25|website=Al Arabiya English|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305082913/https://english.alarabiya.net/News/world/2021/02/25/Armenian-PM-says-attempted-coup-happening-in-the-country-Report|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
{{参见|2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫战争|2020年纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫停火协议}}

在[[2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫战争|2020年納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫戰爭]]期間，[[阿塞拜疆武装力量|亞塞拜然武裝力量]]經過三天的戰鬥，奪取了許多定居點的控制權，包括具有戰略意義的重要城市和納卡地區第二大城[[舒沙|舒沙]]。戰爭最終以亞塞拜然的勝利結束，雙方在俄羅斯總統[[弗拉基米尔·普京|普丁]]的斡旋下簽署了停火協議。根據協議，亞美尼亞和亞塞拜然軍隊將繼續留在原地，直到亞美尼亞軍隊歸還其佔領的納戈爾諾-卡拉巴赫周邊地區（[[克爾巴賈爾區|克爾巴賈爾]]、[[阿格達姆區|阿格達姆區]]和[[拉欽區|拉欽地區]]）給亞塞拜然。亞塞拜然則將保留戰爭期間佔領的所有納卡地區南部領土，並將在其餘的納卡地區部署約2,000名的俄羅斯維和部隊。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Dixon|first=Robyn|date=2020-11-10|title=Cease-fire in Nagorno-Karabakh provokes protests in Armenia, celebrations in Azerbaijan|language=en|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/nagorno-karabakh-ceasefire-armenia-russia-azerbaijan/2020/11/10/b1b9bcc0-231b-11eb-9c4a-0dc6242c4814_story.html|access-date=2020-11-10|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110132331/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/europe/nagorno-karabakh-ceasefire-armenia-russia-azerbaijan/2020/11/10/b1b9bcc0-231b-11eb-9c4a-0dc6242c4814_story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-11-10|title=Armenia, Azerbaijan and Russia sign Nagorno-Karabakh peace deal|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54882564|access-date=2020-11-11|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109235223/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-54882564|dead-url=no}}</ref>在亞塞拜然廣泛慶祝勝利的同時，一些亞美尼亞人迅速走上街頭。抗議者稱總理帕希尼揚為「叛徒」，並要求他下台，廢除停火協議並重新開始戰爭以奪回納卡地區。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tensions persist despite Nagorno-Karabakh peace deal: Live news|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/11/10/tensions-mount-despite-nagorno-karabakh-peace-deal-live-news|accessdate=2020-11-10|last=Qazi|first=Anealla Safdar,Shereena|website=[[Al_Jazeera_English|Al Jazeera English]]|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110100153/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/11/10/tensions-mount-despite-nagorno-karabakh-peace-deal-live-news|dead-url=no}}</ref>

而同時，亞美尼亞国家安全局前局长{{en-link|瓦内强|Artur Vanetsyan}}、亚美尼亚共和党国会前领袖巴格达萨良（Vahram Baghdasaryan）等人因计划暗杀帕希尼扬而被逮捕。對於大規模示威，帕希尼扬表示，自己是在别无选择下签署停火协议，目的是避免国家丧失更多领土，并表示自己願为此承担个人责任，但拒絕辞职<ref>{{cite news |title=【纳卡冲突】亚美尼亚阻止暗杀总理阴谋 前国安局负责人被捕 |url=https://www.dwnews.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83/60218962/%E7%BA%B3%E5%8D%A1%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E4%BA%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%97%E6%9D%80%E6%80%BB%E7%90%86%E9%98%B4%E8%B0%8B%E5%89%8D%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95 |accessdate=2020-11-15 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124002722/https://www.dwnews.com/%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83/60218962/%E7%BA%B3%E5%8D%A1%E5%86%B2%E7%AA%81%E4%BA%9A%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9A%E9%98%BB%E6%AD%A2%E6%9A%97%E6%9D%80%E6%80%BB%E7%90%86%E9%98%B4%E8%B0%8B%E5%89%8D%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%89%E5%B1%80%E8%B4%9F%E8%B4%A3%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

